results.name: Little Posite One XX PS 'Big Bang'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Little Posite One XX PS ‘Big Bang’ brings back a popular outer-space design previously featured on an Air Foamposite One that released during 2018 All-Star Weekend. The nebulous all-over graphic, based on an unreleased 2011 sample of the coveted ‘Galaxy’ iteration of the Air Foamposite One, showcases a swirling blend of blue, orange and violet hues throughout the virtually seamless upper, formed by pouring synthetic liquid into a mold.

Kyrie 7 GS 'BK Black'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Kyrie 7 GS ‘BK Black’ delivers an essential colorway of Kyrie Irving’s seventh signature shoe that pays homage to the Brooklyn Nets. Breathable black mesh is utilized on the upper, complete with TPU ‘fingers’ integrated into the lacing system for a lockdown fit. The mid-top rides on a soft foam midsole, reinforced by a grippy rubber outsole that extends up the sidewalls to offer added traction during quick cuts.

results.story: Built for big kids, the adidas Predator Mutator 20.1 FG J ‘Precision To Blur Pack’ features a vibrant Signal Green finish on a breathable knit textile upper, accented with streaky black lines that convey a sense of movement. An elastic knit collar offers flexible ankle support, while a Demonskin rubber strike zone provides enhanced ball control and touch. Underfoot, firm-ground cleats are strategically placed to deliver superior grip.

Run DMC x Superstar Big Kids '50th Anniversary'
results.story: Celebrating the iconic sneaker’s half-century milestone, the Run DMC x adidas Superstar Big Kids ‘50th Anniversary’ shares the spotlight with the Queens hip hop group that helped fuel the rise of the shell-toed silhouette. The all-leather upper is rendered in a crisp Cloud White finish, contrasted by black serrated three-stripes and a heel tab in Hi-Res Red. Run DMC’s familiar logo adorns the printed tongue tag, its bold typeface repeated on the ‘Superstar’ branding hit on the lateral quarter panel.

results.name: Run DMC x Superstar Little Kids '50th Anniversary'
results.story: The Run DMC x adidas Superstar Little Kids ‘50th Anniversary’ celebrates the iconic silhouette’s half-century birthday with help from the legendary hip hop group who famously wore their shell toes sans laces. The low-top makes use of a leather upper in Cloud White, accented with serrated black three-stripes and a contrasting red heel tab. On the lateral quarter panel, ‘Superstar’ is inscribed using the bold typeface of the classic Run DMC logo, which decorates the sneaker’s tongue and sockliner.

Air Force 1 LV8 PS 'Swoosh Compass'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Air Force 1 LV8 PS ‘Swoosh Compass’ updates the retro low-top with an outdoor-inspired makeover. Unique details give the nod to apparel and equipment used during camping trips, including a hexagonal metal eyelet, a compass graphic on the lateral forefoot and reflective thread woven into the laces. A perforated diamond pattern enlivens the upper, crafted from a blend of genuine and synthetic leather.

results.name: Air Force 1 LV8 GS 'Swoosh Compass'
results.story: Offered in grade school sizing, the Nike Air Force 1 LV8 GS ‘Swoosh Compass’ treats the classic silhouette to a design refresh inspired by outdoor adventures and the tools they require. Unique details include a hexagonal metal eyelet, a compass graphic on the lateral forefoot and a buckled neon yellow strap overlaid across the lace bed. The upper is crafted from real and synthetic leather, embellished with a perforated diamond pattern throughout the toe box and quarter panel.

Air Max 2090 GS 'Black Metallic Gold Star'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Air Max 2090 GS ‘Black Metallic Gold Star’ delivers a simple two-tone colorway of a lifestyle runner based on the Air Max 90. The sneaker’s black mesh upper is enlivened with metallic gold accents on the printed Swoosh and synthetic leather mudguard. An open-hole tongue combines with a pull tab at the heel to provide easy on and off. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a midsole that combines soft foam with a large-volume Max Air unit in the heel.

NMD_R1 J 'All Over Print - Grey Signal Green'
results.story: Designed for big kids, the adidas NMD_R1 J ‘Grey Signal Green’ enlivens the sneaker’s monochrome upper with reflective three-stripes and a subtle all-over print. The latter comprises repeating lines of the phrase ‘The Brand with the Three Stripes’ rendered in multilingual text, which extend to the back half of the Boost midsole. Here, the tagline is inscribed in Signal Green lettering, matching a flash of color on the forefoot EVA plug.

results.name: NMD_R1 J 'All Over Print - Light Grey Signal Pink'
results.story: Built for big kids, the adidas NMD_R1 J ‘Light Grey Signal Pink’ treats the lifestyle runner to a neutral palette and unexpected details. The latter includes reflective three-stripes and a tonal all-over print made up of multilingual iterations of the phrase ‘The Brand with the Three Stripes.’ The same tagline is repeated in Signal Pink text across the back half of the full-length Boost midsole, equipped with EVA plugs for a stable ride.

Air More Uptempo GS 'Peace, Love, and Basketball'
results.story: Made for big kids, the Nike Air More Uptempo GS ‘Peace, Love, and Basketball’ updates the retro hoops shoe with a distinctive color scheme inspired by San Francisco in the late ‘60s. Signature ‘AIR’ branding is spelled out in black leather trimmed in gold, allowing the outsized letters to stand out against a royal blue leather backdrop. A foam midsole with visible Max Air cushioning provides a smooth ride. Inside the shoe, the sockliner features a psychedelic ‘Peace, Love, Basketball’ graphic.

Tensor J 'Black Signal Pink'
results.story: Offered in big kid sizing, the adidas Tensor J ‘Black Signal Pink’ showcase a simple two-tone palette on a versatile training shoe built for indoor and outdoor play. Dual hook-and-loop straps secure the upper, constructed from breathable black mesh with tonal synthetic overlays. Decorative stitching in Signal Pink is matched by signature three-stripes and an adidas branding hit atop the tongue. Plush cushioning arrives via a stacked Eva midsole in a crisp white finish.

results.name: Tensor J 'Legacy Blue'
results.story: Built for big kids, the adidas Tensor J ‘Legacy Blue’ rides on a plush EVA midsole that also doubles as the outsole, featuring flex grooves for a smooth, comfortable ride. Up top, the sneaker’s breathable mesh construction is rendered in a subdued blue finish. Tonal synthetic overlays provide added durability and support at the toe and heel. A neon pop of Signal Green distinguishes the pull tab at the heel, which works with the hook-and-loop straps to provide easy on and off.

results.name: Air Max 90 GS 'Black Volt Racer Blue'
results.story: Developed for big kids, the Nike Air Max 90 GS ‘Black Volt Racer Blue’ features a simple palette that pairs a neutral base with vibrant pops of color. The latter takes the form of a royal blue patent leather Swoosh and TPU accents in Nike’s signature Volt. The rest of the upper is constructed from black mesh with tonal synthetic leather overlays, all of which is supported by a white foam midsole with visible Max Air cushioning under the heel.

results.name: Kyrie Flytrap 4 GS 'Deep Royal Blue'
results.colorway: Blue Void/Deep Royal Blue/Lucky Green/Speed Yellow
results.story: Tailored for big kids the Nike Kyrie Flytrap 4 GS ‘Deep Royal Blue’ delivers a lightweight performance hoops shoe built for speed and agility. A rich blue finish is applied to the breathable textile upper, reinforced with a no-sew toe bumper and synthetic leather paneling that wraps around the heel. A contrasting white foam midsole is wrapped up by the high-traction rubber outsole, enabling quick cuts and pivots on the hardwood.
